WEBVTT

00:07:26.480 --> 00:07:30.896
Pamoja na njia hii, nimejifunza
mafunzo ya thamani.

00:07:30.920 --> 00:07:34.016
Watu waliotuma
barua za chuki ni wafanyakazi,

00:07:34.040 --> 00:07:36.336
waume, wake,

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:38.170
wazazi kama wewe na mimi.

00:07:38.520 --> 00:07:42.856
Sisemi kua tabia
yao inakubalika,

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:47.616
lakini nimejifunza kujiweka mbali
na maoni ya chuki

00:07:47.640 --> 00:07:53.240
bila kujiweka mbali na mtu anayetoa
hayo maoni.

00:07:55.240 --> 00:07:57.296
Nimegundua

00:07:57.320 --> 00:08:02.216
kua watu ninaowatembelea wana
uwoga kama tu wa watu wasiowajua